WEBVTT

00:01:40.690 --> 00:01:45.890
[THE DEVIL BETWEEN US]

00:01:45.970 --> 00:01:48.930
[Episode 9]

00:01:49.009 --> 00:01:53.560
[Zebin Billiard Room]

00:02:13.120 --> 00:02:13.720
Excuse me,

00:02:14.960 --> 00:02:15.960
is this whole area

00:02:17.000 --> 00:02:20.000
the housing complex
for the old paper mill?

00:02:20.370 --> 00:02:21.500
This whole area is.

00:02:21.530 --> 00:02:22.460
That area isn't.

00:02:27.240 --> 00:02:30.240
Wasn't there a big case here a while ago?

00:02:30.960 --> 00:02:32.490
Guns were involved, right?

00:02:34.280 --> 00:02:35.340
Are you a reporter?

00:02:37.120 --> 00:02:38.450
I'm an online reporter.

00:02:38.690 --> 00:02:39.370
I get it.

00:02:40.570 --> 00:02:42.370
You've come to the right person.

00:02:42.680 --> 00:02:44.240
I'm a key figure.

00:02:45.079 --> 00:02:45.870
Come here.

00:02:46.150 --> 00:02:47.000
Have a seat.

00:02:48.970 --> 00:02:49.460
Come.

00:02:49.610 --> 00:02:51.140
Let me tell you all about it.

00:02:52.910 --> 00:02:53.590
At the time,

00:02:53.960 --> 00:02:56.560
I bought the police half an hour.

00:02:56.970 --> 00:03:00.300
Otherwise, they wouldn't
have solved the case so smoothly.

00:03:13.400 --> 00:03:14.200
What's wrong?

00:03:15.520 --> 00:03:16.120
Um...

00:03:16.430 --> 00:03:18.900
Do you know Director Yao
from the City Bureau?

00:03:18.900 --> 00:03:19.430
No, I don't.

00:03:19.430 --> 00:03:21.910
If I knew him, I'd have transferred
out of here long ago.

00:03:21.910 --> 00:03:23.000
That's strange.

00:03:23.560 --> 00:03:24.910
Captain Li just called me.

00:03:24.910 --> 00:03:27.620
He said Director Yao
wants you to go see him in the city.

00:03:27.620 --> 00:03:28.680
Did he say what it's about?

00:03:28.680 --> 00:03:29.210
No.

00:03:30.730 --> 00:03:32.980
Could it be about Quan's case?

00:03:33.190 --> 00:03:33.750
You did a good job

00:03:33.750 --> 00:03:35.610
and caught the City Bureau's eye.

00:03:36.360 --> 00:03:37.750
Really? That would be great.

00:03:37.750 --> 00:03:38.190
Really?

00:03:38.190 --> 00:03:39.320
That would be great.

00:03:39.840 --> 00:03:41.240
Don't get your hopes up.

00:03:41.380 --> 00:03:42.490
If it were about a transfer,

00:03:42.490 --> 00:03:44.220
Li would have told me directly.

00:03:45.630 --> 00:03:46.890
Who do you think you are

00:03:46.920 --> 00:03:48.590
to have Director Yao
talk to you personally?

00:03:48.590 --> 00:03:49.280
Yeah.

00:03:49.590 --> 00:03:50.590
Be mentally prepared.

00:03:50.590 --> 00:03:52.450
There might be strings attached.

00:03:53.079 --> 00:03:54.590
Strings attached, fine.

00:03:54.590 --> 00:03:55.240
Anyway,

00:03:55.430 --> 00:03:57.280
as long as my son can
go to middle school in the city,

00:03:57.280 --> 00:03:58.540
I'm okay with a pay cut.

00:04:00.190 --> 00:04:01.130
You're really set on this?

00:04:01.130 --> 00:04:01.650
Yes.

00:04:03.230 --> 00:04:04.000
Go back.

00:04:05.230 --> 00:04:06.140
Is that it?

00:04:06.430 --> 00:04:07.630
This is small to you?

00:04:10.960 --> 00:04:12.150
So this shop

00:04:12.940 --> 00:04:15.030
used to be a drug den.

00:04:16.060 --> 00:04:17.459
Now that the shop is gone,

00:04:18.829 --> 00:04:20.630
will those addicts
who can't find their fix

00:04:20.630 --> 00:04:23.000
come around here and cause trouble?

00:04:23.680 --> 00:04:24.120
Well,

00:04:24.480 --> 00:04:26.630
I haven't heard about that.

00:04:27.900 --> 00:04:30.030
That means there are still some people

00:04:30.290 --> 00:04:31.680
who haven't got the news

00:04:32.030 --> 00:04:34.230
and will keep coming to look for drugs.

00:04:44.310 --> 00:04:44.800
Buddy.

00:04:48.240 --> 00:04:48.840
What's up?

00:04:49.210 --> 00:04:50.120
Here to buy candy?

00:04:50.120 --> 00:04:51.380
This place got busted.

00:04:52.159 --> 00:04:52.850
Do you want some?

00:04:52.850 --> 00:04:53.730
I have a source.

00:04:54.800 --> 00:04:55.480
No, no.

00:04:55.750 --> 00:04:56.310
Come on, have some.

00:04:56.310 --> 00:04:56.780
No.

00:05:01.530 --> 00:05:02.410
Coming.

00:05:50.240 --> 00:05:51.370
Want a foot massage?

00:05:56.750 --> 00:05:57.390
Eight Wan.

00:05:57.960 --> 00:05:58.680
Two Bamboo.

00:05:59.640 --> 00:06:00.230
Pong.

00:06:04.580 --> 00:06:05.220
Pong.

00:06:12.520 --> 00:06:13.350
Cao Jinchuan!

00:06:16.310 --> 00:06:17.110
Cao Jinchuan!

00:06:21.120 --> 00:06:21.720
Don't run!

00:06:23.130 --> 00:06:23.720
Who's it?

00:06:24.690 --> 00:06:25.490
Cao Jinchuan.

00:06:28.800 --> 00:06:29.310
Stop running!

00:06:29.310 --> 00:06:30.240
Stop running!

00:06:32.520 --> 00:06:33.320
Cao Jinchuan!

00:06:38.680 --> 00:06:39.310
Cao Jinchuan.

00:06:39.310 --> 00:06:40.080
Cao Jinchuan.

00:06:40.080 --> 00:06:40.680
Stay back.

00:06:42.070 --> 00:06:43.470
Or I'll beat you to death!

00:06:45.020 --> 00:06:45.820
Cao Jinchuan!

00:06:48.240 --> 00:06:49.170
Move!

00:06:51.510 --> 00:06:52.310
Cao Jinchuan!

00:06:54.090 --> 00:06:55.150
What are you doing?

00:07:07.460 --> 00:07:08.680
Why do you run when you see me?

00:07:08.680 --> 00:07:10.680
You were chasing me. Of course I ran.

00:07:10.830 --> 00:07:12.160
Do you even know who I am?

00:07:12.360 --> 00:07:12.960
You're...

00:07:13.800 --> 00:07:14.680
a cop?

00:07:14.870 --> 00:07:16.000
Or a debt collector?

00:07:16.250 --> 00:07:16.970
Look closely.

00:07:16.970 --> 00:07:18.210
See who I am.

00:07:20.330 --> 00:07:21.140
Look.

00:07:26.970 --> 00:07:28.930
Are you crazy?

00:07:32.680 --> 00:07:33.810
Just for 1,000 yuan,

00:07:34.510 --> 00:07:36.370
you were chasing me desperately.

00:07:37.360 --> 00:07:39.490
-Are you out of your mind?
-Don't move.

00:07:40.580 --> 00:07:41.310
Don't move.

00:07:43.990 --> 00:07:45.140
You took my money,

00:07:45.659 --> 00:07:47.440
but haven't taken me to the guy yet.

00:07:47.440 --> 00:07:48.320
What guy?

00:07:50.050 --> 00:07:50.760
The...

00:07:51.430 --> 00:07:52.760
guy selling that stuff.

00:07:54.790 --> 00:07:56.710
Didn't you hear what I told the cops?

00:07:56.710 --> 00:07:58.000
I saw you were clueless,

00:07:58.000 --> 00:07:59.040
so I tricked you.

00:07:59.310 --> 00:08:01.710
How would I know
people who sell that stuff?

00:08:01.720 --> 00:08:02.390
Look, dude.

00:08:02.720 --> 00:08:03.240
I...

00:08:03.430 --> 00:08:04.830
I'll give you back the money.

00:08:04.830 --> 00:08:05.360
Okay?

00:08:05.390 --> 00:08:06.650
I don't want the money.

00:08:07.000 --> 00:08:08.190
I want to find the person.

00:08:08.190 --> 00:08:10.390
I don't know them.

00:08:11.040 --> 00:08:13.300
Then why did you
go to the bubble tea shop?

00:08:19.830 --> 00:08:20.360
I...

00:08:20.560 --> 00:08:22.310
I was just passing the bubble tea shop.

00:08:22.310 --> 00:08:23.370
Isn't that normal?

00:08:51.190 --> 00:08:51.880
Bao...

00:08:51.930 --> 00:08:53.130
Bao agreed to see you.

00:08:53.910 --> 00:08:55.360
I'll take you there tonight.

00:08:55.360 --> 00:08:56.270
Don't worry.

00:08:56.390 --> 00:08:57.510
Bao's got everything you need.

00:08:57.510 --> 00:08:58.550
You'll be satisfied.

00:08:58.550 --> 00:09:00.310
Ever since that Quan died,

00:09:00.330 --> 00:09:01.670
many people are out of supply

00:09:01.670 --> 00:09:03.270
and have all come to Bao now.

00:09:03.510 --> 00:09:04.840
But Bao has been very busy.

00:09:04.840 --> 00:09:05.550
I don't introduce just anyone.

00:09:05.550 --> 00:09:06.450
Who's Quan?

00:09:08.910 --> 00:09:10.040
You don't know Quan?

00:09:10.360 --> 00:09:12.240
But you found the bubble tea shop.

00:09:13.840 --> 00:09:14.440
You know,

00:09:14.680 --> 00:09:16.010
the huge news recently.

00:09:16.020 --> 00:09:18.280
The gunfight at the old paper mill dorms.

00:09:18.280 --> 00:09:19.680
The guy who died was Quan.

00:09:19.790 --> 00:09:20.910
I saw the news.

00:09:20.930 --> 00:09:22.170
I don't know his name.

00:09:24.000 --> 00:09:24.790
Ken,

00:09:26.270 --> 00:09:27.510
can you tell me

00:09:27.670 --> 00:09:29.080
what exactly you need?

00:09:29.270 --> 00:09:30.000
How much?

00:09:30.510 --> 00:09:31.720
I'll give Bao a heads-up.

00:09:31.720 --> 00:09:32.920
So he can get it ready.

00:09:33.670 --> 00:09:34.790
I'm not buying.

00:09:37.720 --> 00:09:38.630
Selling?

00:09:43.890 --> 00:09:44.890
You're crazy.

00:09:45.460 --> 00:09:46.780
Are you out of your mind?

00:09:46.780 --> 00:09:48.180
Put that away.

00:09:52.170 --> 00:09:53.150
You're out of your mind.

00:09:53.150 --> 00:09:53.910
I can't take you to see Bao.

00:09:53.910 --> 00:09:55.150
You'll get me killed.

00:09:56.710 --> 00:09:57.240
Let go!

00:10:20.950 --> 00:10:22.270
You know Jungle Chess?

00:10:23.660 --> 00:10:24.700
In Jungle Chess,

00:10:26.730 --> 00:10:27.540
the Elephant

00:10:27.720 --> 00:10:28.550
can eat

00:10:29.170 --> 00:10:30.000
the Lion, Tiger, Leopard,

00:10:30.000 --> 00:10:30.860
Wolf, Dog, Cat—

00:10:31.670 --> 00:10:32.870
but not the Rat.

00:10:33.310 --> 00:10:35.110
But the Rat can eat the Elephant.

00:10:38.230 --> 00:10:39.680
Right now, I'm a Rat

00:10:40.220 --> 00:10:41.620
that's not afraid to die.

00:10:53.550 --> 00:10:54.080
Ken.

00:10:54.790 --> 00:10:55.240
Ken,

00:10:56.510 --> 00:10:57.510
I'm afraid to die.

00:10:59.390 --> 00:11:00.270
I know.

00:11:09.380 --> 00:11:11.450
[Haizhou Public Security Bureau]

00:11:28.560 --> 00:11:29.200
Come in.

00:11:29.480 --> 00:11:30.150
[Yao Feng, Deputy Director
of Haizhou Public Security Bureau]

00:11:30.150 --> 00:11:30.950
Director Yao,

00:11:32.360 --> 00:11:34.080
I'm Hu Wenjing from
the Criminal Investigation Brigade

00:11:34.080 --> 00:11:35.150
of Nuanfeng County Public Security Bureau.

00:11:35.150 --> 00:11:36.060
Badge number...

00:11:36.060 --> 00:11:36.890
No need for introductions.

00:11:36.890 --> 00:11:37.550
Have a seat.

00:11:40.360 --> 00:11:41.470
I asked you here

00:11:41.500 --> 00:11:43.310
to talk about your transfer.

00:11:45.030 --> 00:11:46.670
Your resume is excellent.

00:11:46.690 --> 00:11:47.570
Regarding

00:11:47.750 --> 00:11:48.790
your transfer to the Municipal Bureau,

00:11:48.790 --> 00:11:50.240
your unit's HR department and we

00:11:50.240 --> 00:11:51.440
are all in agreement.

00:11:52.350 --> 00:11:55.680
But something unexpected came up
during the file transfer.

00:11:56.430 --> 00:11:57.970
You know this better than I do,

00:11:57.970 --> 00:11:59.170
so I won't elaborate.

00:12:00.440 --> 00:12:01.910
I just want to ask,

00:12:03.060 --> 00:12:05.790
do you still want to come
to the Municipal Bureau?

00:12:06.510 --> 00:12:07.150
Yes, sir.

00:12:07.150 --> 00:12:07.840
I do.

00:12:10.600 --> 00:12:11.400
Director Yao.

00:12:15.920 --> 00:12:17.400
Why beat around the bush?

00:12:17.420 --> 00:12:19.220
Why did you really bring me here?

00:12:19.330 --> 00:12:20.930
I read Jin Longzheng's report,

00:12:20.930 --> 00:12:22.880
and I talked to Qin and the others.

00:12:23.290 --> 00:12:24.670
We think you're highly capable,

00:12:24.670 --> 00:12:25.790
have a good rapport with the community,

00:12:25.790 --> 00:12:27.450
and are excellent all around.

00:12:27.740 --> 00:12:28.720
So I was thinking...

00:12:28.720 --> 00:12:29.730
We're busy here.

00:12:29.760 --> 00:12:31.040
Let's cut to the chase.

00:12:32.070 --> 00:12:32.600
Alright.

00:12:33.390 --> 00:12:35.360
I heard you want to transfer here

00:12:35.460 --> 00:12:38.390
so your two sons can
attend middle school in the city.

00:12:39.030 --> 00:12:39.630
Yes.

00:12:41.480 --> 00:12:42.840
Whether it's getting into the bureau

00:12:42.840 --> 00:12:44.240
or your kids' schooling,

00:12:44.330 --> 00:12:45.460
I can help with both.

00:12:45.910 --> 00:12:46.720
But,

00:12:47.150 --> 00:12:48.350
I have one condition.

00:12:50.270 --> 00:12:51.390
Once you're in,

00:12:51.800 --> 00:12:53.400
you join our Narcotics Unit.

00:13:09.120 --> 00:13:09.780
Right here.

00:13:24.850 --> 00:13:25.490
Ken,

00:13:26.560 --> 00:13:27.890
wait here a second.

00:13:28.320 --> 00:13:29.780
I need to talk to Bao first.

00:13:30.150 --> 00:13:32.150
He doesn't know you're here to sell.

00:13:34.910 --> 00:13:36.160
Don't make me wait too long.

00:13:36.160 --> 00:13:37.020
It'll be quick.

00:13:45.960 --> 00:13:46.910
Is that Chuan?

00:13:48.560 --> 00:13:49.080
Bao.

00:13:56.430 --> 00:13:57.310
Bao.

00:13:58.120 --> 00:13:59.380
Where's the guy you mentioned?

00:13:59.380 --> 00:14:00.980
I told him to wait in the yard.

00:14:01.920 --> 00:14:03.240
What does he want to buy?

00:14:03.240 --> 00:14:05.150
Weed, meth,

00:14:05.630 --> 00:14:07.080
ecstasy, or Ketamine?

00:14:08.270 --> 00:14:08.670
He...

00:14:09.130 --> 00:14:11.200
That idiot isn't here to buy goods.

00:14:11.230 --> 00:14:12.750
He's here to sell.

00:14:13.200 --> 00:14:14.000
What the hell?

00:14:16.070 --> 00:14:17.630
Are you stupid?

00:14:18.220 --> 00:14:18.880
It's not me.

00:14:19.080 --> 00:14:19.720
He...

00:14:20.070 --> 00:14:22.750
We just stick to selling fakes.

00:14:22.770 --> 00:14:23.840
Whoever buys our stuff

00:14:23.840 --> 00:14:25.030
won't go to the cops to report us, right?

00:14:25.030 --> 00:14:25.390
Yeah.

00:14:25.480 --> 00:14:27.360
Taking their money is practically
doing the world a favor.

00:14:27.360 --> 00:14:28.550
I know that.

00:14:28.550 --> 00:14:30.720
So why'd you hook up with
someone selling the real stuff?

00:14:30.720 --> 00:14:31.120
I...

00:14:31.240 --> 00:14:31.510
He...

00:14:31.510 --> 00:14:33.360
Don't you know
how serious drug dealing is?

00:14:33.360 --> 00:14:34.440
I know.

00:14:34.440 --> 00:14:35.390
We can't throw

00:14:35.390 --> 00:14:36.320
our lives away this young.

00:14:36.320 --> 00:14:36.840
Yes.

00:14:36.870 --> 00:14:38.180
Get him out of here.

00:14:38.200 --> 00:14:38.630
Get him out.

00:14:38.630 --> 00:14:39.840
Wait,

00:14:47.440 --> 00:14:49.040
I came to you for help.

00:14:49.160 --> 00:14:50.230
Help me

00:14:50.400 --> 00:14:51.140
get rid of him.

00:14:51.140 --> 00:14:51.900
He hit you,

00:14:52.110 --> 00:14:53.510
and you brought him here?

00:14:55.560 --> 00:14:56.870
Figure out a way to send him away.

00:14:56.870 --> 00:14:57.670
What can I do?

00:14:57.670 --> 00:14:59.360
Just say I don't buy from strangers.

00:14:59.360 --> 00:14:59.870
Let him leave.

00:14:59.870 --> 00:15:01.910
He won't leave until you see him.

00:15:01.910 --> 00:15:03.150
What do you want me to do?

00:15:03.150 --> 00:15:04.840
Think of a way to kick him out.

00:15:04.840 --> 00:15:05.790
Just say his goods are no good.

00:15:05.790 --> 00:15:07.650
But I'll get beaten up if I go back.

00:15:13.080 --> 00:15:13.670
Who's it?

00:15:14.840 --> 00:15:15.500
This is Ken.

00:15:16.550 --> 00:15:17.030
Bao.

00:15:17.200 --> 00:15:17.840
Ken,

00:15:18.030 --> 00:15:19.890
didn't I tell you to wait outside?

00:15:22.000 --> 00:15:22.870
Uh,

00:15:23.370 --> 00:15:24.720
let him come in.

00:15:42.870 --> 00:15:44.330
Which crew do you run with?

00:15:45.790 --> 00:15:46.840
I'm not with anyone.

00:15:46.840 --> 00:15:47.880
Just here to sell.

00:15:51.550 --> 00:15:52.250
Have a seat.

00:15:56.600 --> 00:15:58.050
Get him a chair.

00:16:03.080 --> 00:16:03.790
Let me do it.

00:16:08.990 --> 00:16:09.870
So,

00:16:10.590 --> 00:16:11.310
Chuan

00:16:11.960 --> 00:16:13.090
told me everything.

00:16:13.510 --> 00:16:14.440
Dude, you...

00:16:15.480 --> 00:16:16.740
have the wrong person.

00:16:17.630 --> 00:16:18.360
I

00:16:18.790 --> 00:16:19.550
only sell.

00:16:20.270 --> 00:16:21.000
I don't buy.

00:16:21.840 --> 00:16:22.320
Right.

00:16:22.340 --> 00:16:23.670
I already talked to Bao.

00:16:23.840 --> 00:16:24.770
If you don't buy,

00:16:25.030 --> 00:16:25.960
what do you sell?

00:16:27.080 --> 00:16:29.270
I don't buy from strangers.

00:16:30.200 --> 00:16:31.400
Go find someone else.

00:16:31.840 --> 00:16:32.110
Yes.

00:16:32.110 --> 00:16:32.770
See him out.

00:16:32.870 --> 00:16:33.480
Ken,

00:16:33.480 --> 00:16:33.840
you just...

00:16:33.840 --> 00:16:34.390
How about this?

00:16:34.390 --> 00:16:35.390
Take a look first.

00:16:35.470 --> 00:16:36.710
See what I've got.

00:16:44.270 --> 00:16:45.600
Calm down.

00:16:46.670 --> 00:16:47.720
There's two of us.

00:16:48.270 --> 00:16:49.460
You're alone.

00:16:49.870 --> 00:16:50.870
If it comes to a fight,

00:16:50.870 --> 00:16:52.720
you might not win.

00:17:02.440 --> 00:17:03.440
Stand over there.

00:17:06.829 --> 00:17:07.349
Alright.

00:17:07.349 --> 00:17:08.510
Take the goods out.

00:17:09.200 --> 00:17:10.460
Let me see the quality.

00:17:46.470 --> 00:17:47.560
Faker!

00:17:50.610 --> 00:17:51.210
Dude,

00:17:51.600 --> 00:17:52.930
you're way too amateur.

00:17:53.260 --> 00:17:55.260
You take some rose sea salt

00:17:55.530 --> 00:17:56.640
and dare to pass it off as drugs?

00:17:56.640 --> 00:17:58.170
Can you make money off this?

00:17:59.590 --> 00:18:00.030
Look.

00:18:01.150 --> 00:18:01.830
It's fake?

