00:33:06.310 --> 00:33:07.550
You can call me Jin.

00:33:07.660 --> 00:33:08.490
Jin.

00:33:08.720 --> 00:33:09.200
I see.

00:33:09.350 --> 00:33:10.310
I'll go cook a couple more dishes.

00:33:10.310 --> 00:33:11.110
Stay for dinner.

00:33:11.110 --> 00:33:11.640
No need. He's leaving.

00:33:11.640 --> 00:33:12.240
Right now.

00:33:12.240 --> 00:33:13.510
Yes, I'm leaving now.

00:33:13.530 --> 00:33:14.450
Make yourself at home.

00:33:14.450 --> 00:33:15.850
Since you're here,

00:33:15.870 --> 00:33:17.630
you've gotta try my cooking.

00:33:17.750 --> 00:33:19.000
Really, you must.

00:33:19.030 --> 00:33:19.880
This is the first time

00:33:19.880 --> 00:33:22.190
a male colleague of Wenjing's
has ever come over.

00:33:22.190 --> 00:33:22.870
Just wait.

00:33:27.310 --> 00:33:28.370
It won't take long.

00:33:38.890 --> 00:33:39.820
Have some water.

00:33:45.520 --> 00:33:46.090
Go on.

00:33:48.810 --> 00:33:50.650
So, Wu came to you, didn't he?

00:33:51.720 --> 00:33:53.050
You're well-informed.

00:33:54.270 --> 00:33:56.530
Did he ask you to join the Narcotics Unit?

00:33:56.930 --> 00:33:57.510
He mentioned it.

00:33:57.510 --> 00:33:58.640
Don't listen to him.

00:33:58.640 --> 00:33:59.770
Narcotics isn't for you.

00:33:59.770 --> 00:34:01.450
How is it for you but not for me?

00:34:02.070 --> 00:34:03.270
Look, ability-wise,

00:34:03.480 --> 00:34:04.740
you could be my mentor.

00:34:05.230 --> 00:34:07.220
But narcotics work
is dangerous and grueling.

00:34:07.220 --> 00:34:08.570
Not for a single mother.

00:34:08.960 --> 00:34:09.840
Especially one with two kids

00:34:09.840 --> 00:34:11.389
and an elderly parent to care for.

00:34:11.389 --> 00:34:13.050
And they're all here locally.

00:34:13.960 --> 00:34:16.489
He said he could help
with my kids' schooling.

00:34:18.600 --> 00:34:20.400
No. 3 Middle School
isn't hard to get into.

00:34:20.400 --> 00:34:22.060
We can figure out another way.

00:34:22.400 --> 00:34:23.300
Why are you meddling so much?

00:34:23.300 --> 00:34:24.659
Why do you keep interfering
in my business?

00:34:24.659 --> 00:34:25.730
Mind your own business.

00:34:25.730 --> 00:34:27.469
Stop running around on that gimpy leg.

00:34:27.469 --> 00:34:28.710
Rest more when you can.

00:34:28.710 --> 00:34:29.370
Go back now.

00:34:32.150 --> 00:34:32.670
Okay.

00:34:34.510 --> 00:34:35.510
Just think

00:34:35.510 --> 00:34:36.710
about what I said.

00:34:36.850 --> 00:34:37.290
Okay.

00:34:37.360 --> 00:34:38.150
And when you

00:34:38.150 --> 00:34:39.550
call Wu next time,

00:34:39.550 --> 00:34:40.480
let me know.

00:34:41.150 --> 00:34:41.800
I don't need to tell you.

00:34:41.800 --> 00:34:42.860
I'll make the call.

00:34:43.690 --> 00:34:44.409
Alright.

00:34:45.030 --> 00:34:45.590
Dad,

00:34:45.989 --> 00:34:47.449
Jin Longzheng is leaving.

00:34:47.870 --> 00:34:49.199
Uncle, I'm heading off.

00:34:49.730 --> 00:34:50.920
Jin, don't go.

00:34:50.920 --> 00:34:52.070
I'm halfway through cooking.

00:34:52.070 --> 00:34:53.190
Who's gonna eat all this if you leave?

00:34:53.190 --> 00:34:54.150
He's got things to do.

00:34:54.150 --> 00:34:54.630
No way.

00:34:54.630 --> 00:34:55.480
I really have things to do.

00:34:55.480 --> 00:34:56.110
You have to eat.

00:34:56.110 --> 00:34:56.710
Hurry.

00:34:57.230 --> 00:34:58.440
Listen to me.

00:34:58.710 --> 00:35:00.030
You must stay for dinner.

00:35:00.030 --> 00:35:00.410
Sit.

00:35:00.430 --> 00:35:01.060
Come on.

00:35:01.150 --> 00:35:01.880
Ming, Zhi,

00:35:02.150 --> 00:35:03.480
keep our guest company.

00:35:03.560 --> 00:35:04.770
I'll be right back.

00:35:05.150 --> 00:35:06.280
This dish has been touched.

00:35:06.280 --> 00:35:06.670
No good.

00:35:06.670 --> 00:35:07.230
It hasn't.

00:35:07.230 --> 00:35:07.590
It's fine.

00:35:07.590 --> 00:35:08.360
Untouched.

00:35:08.760 --> 00:35:09.230
This one's been touched.

00:35:09.230 --> 00:35:10.280
Give me a hand.

00:35:10.740 --> 00:35:11.300
Sit down.

00:35:11.440 --> 00:35:12.320
Just sit.

00:35:12.360 --> 00:35:13.030
Sit.

00:35:13.550 --> 00:35:15.210
Sorry for the trouble, Uncle.

00:35:15.320 --> 00:35:15.960
Just wait.

00:35:15.960 --> 00:35:16.760
Almost ready.

00:35:17.180 --> 00:35:18.590
What are you doing here?

00:35:18.590 --> 00:35:19.760
This one's really untouched.

00:35:19.760 --> 00:35:20.710
This one's been touched too.

00:35:20.710 --> 00:35:22.480
We can't serve this to a guest.

00:35:24.990 --> 00:35:25.850
He's handsome.

00:35:26.210 --> 00:35:27.410
I like the look of him.

00:35:28.110 --> 00:35:29.110
Is he your colleague?

00:35:29.110 --> 00:35:29.670
Where's he from?

00:35:29.670 --> 00:35:30.480
City bureau.

00:35:30.480 --> 00:35:31.670
Colleague for now.

00:35:32.610 --> 00:35:34.340
If your transfer works out,

00:35:34.360 --> 00:35:36.300
you'll be together every day
at the city bureau.

00:35:36.300 --> 00:35:36.840
Oh my goodness.

00:35:36.840 --> 00:35:38.070
He's like 7 or 8 years younger than me.

00:35:38.070 --> 00:35:39.590
Don't play matchmaker.

00:35:39.590 --> 00:35:40.280
You're messing around.

00:35:40.280 --> 00:35:41.360
Sweetie,

00:35:42.110 --> 00:35:43.920
you wouldn't be losing out.

00:35:52.110 --> 00:35:53.800
Who exactly are you?

00:35:57.230 --> 00:35:58.680
I'm the champion of the Haizhou

00:35:58.680 --> 00:36:01.140
Police Academy's martial arts tournament.

00:36:02.320 --> 00:36:03.110
Seriously?

00:36:03.300 --> 00:36:04.960
You really know martial arts?

00:36:04.960 --> 00:36:06.020
I know kickboxing.

00:36:06.110 --> 00:36:07.320
Can you teach us?

00:36:08.000 --> 00:36:08.880
Teach you?

00:36:09.590 --> 00:36:10.360
Sure.

00:36:11.230 --> 00:36:12.730
You'll have to eat all your food first.

00:36:12.730 --> 00:36:13.860
Then I'll teach you.

00:36:22.590 --> 00:36:23.400
Dad.

00:37:09.190 --> 00:37:10.950
Where did this egg custard come from?

00:37:10.950 --> 00:37:12.310
I made it myself.

00:37:13.230 --> 00:37:14.440
Didn't I already make

00:37:14.440 --> 00:37:15.920
your meals before I left?

00:37:16.880 --> 00:37:18.410
Why'd you make egg custard?

00:37:18.480 --> 00:37:19.340
Who taught you?

00:37:19.360 --> 00:37:20.780
You used the pot—it's so heavy.

00:37:20.780 --> 00:37:21.770
The stove is so high.

00:37:21.770 --> 00:37:23.360
What if you burned yourself lighting it?

00:37:23.360 --> 00:37:24.420
It's so dangerous.

00:37:28.220 --> 00:37:30.490
You've been out all day.

00:37:30.550 --> 00:37:33.670
I wanted you to come home to hot food.

00:38:16.140 --> 00:38:17.140
It's really good.

00:38:17.710 --> 00:38:19.840
Eat more if you like it.

00:38:30.840 --> 00:38:32.670
Dad, what's wrong?

00:38:40.360 --> 00:38:41.560
I'm just thinking...

00:38:43.000 --> 00:38:44.590
Doing bad things is so hard.

00:38:46.650 --> 00:38:48.480
Aren't we good people?

00:38:48.770 --> 00:38:50.730
Why do we have to do bad things?

00:39:17.150 --> 00:39:17.840
Eat more.

00:39:18.920 --> 00:39:20.150
Come on, sit.

00:39:20.630 --> 00:39:21.110
Jin,

00:39:21.590 --> 00:39:22.840
I heard you

00:39:23.070 --> 00:39:24.000
got hurt a bit.

00:39:24.020 --> 00:39:24.840
Are you better now?

00:39:24.840 --> 00:39:25.570
Much better.

00:39:25.760 --> 00:39:26.510
Well, did you

00:39:26.770 --> 00:39:29.370
have some IV fluids,
anti-inflammatories...

00:39:30.800 --> 00:39:31.930
I can drink a little.

00:39:33.550 --> 00:39:34.550
I'll get the wine.

00:39:35.910 --> 00:39:36.510
One more dish.

00:39:36.510 --> 00:39:37.810
How can we eat all this?

00:39:39.880 --> 00:39:41.810
Why are you behaving so well today?

00:39:42.400 --> 00:39:44.400
Mom, look, we finished everything.

00:39:44.510 --> 00:39:45.640
We'll do the dishes.

00:39:46.260 --> 00:39:48.120
It's easy for men to communicate.

00:39:49.250 --> 00:39:51.080
Brothers do communicate well.

00:39:51.590 --> 00:39:53.250
Let me see how you wash dishes.

00:39:55.110 --> 00:39:55.670
Here.

00:39:56.110 --> 00:39:56.550
Let me.

00:39:56.550 --> 00:39:57.110
I got it.

00:39:57.110 --> 00:39:57.710
No, no.

00:39:57.980 --> 00:39:59.290
It's your first time here.

00:39:59.290 --> 00:40:00.210
You're a guest.

00:40:00.590 --> 00:40:01.190
Let me.

00:40:01.290 --> 00:40:01.810
Here.

00:40:21.120 --> 00:40:21.810
Jiajia.

00:40:22.210 --> 00:40:22.730
Come.

00:40:26.920 --> 00:40:27.590
Sit here.

00:40:29.350 --> 00:40:31.140
I want to talk to you.

00:40:37.710 --> 00:40:38.590
I know.

00:40:38.830 --> 00:40:39.620
Jiajia,

00:40:40.130 --> 00:40:42.420
compared to many other kids,

00:40:43.320 --> 00:40:44.180
you're smarter

00:40:44.550 --> 00:40:45.610
and more sensible.

00:40:47.070 --> 00:40:48.980
So I usually try to treat you

00:40:49.180 --> 00:40:50.430
like a grown-up

00:40:50.450 --> 00:40:51.870
and discuss things with you.

00:40:51.870 --> 00:40:52.540
Right?

00:40:54.420 --> 00:40:57.280
Do you understand
what's going on at home right now?

00:40:58.900 --> 00:40:59.900
Good.

00:41:00.740 --> 00:41:01.530
My

00:41:01.950 --> 00:41:04.240
No.1 task right now is to make money.

00:41:06.000 --> 00:41:07.440
Only if I make money

00:41:07.550 --> 00:41:10.070
can we keep living

00:41:10.920 --> 00:41:12.250
and treat your illness.

00:41:13.790 --> 00:41:15.580
But I can't let anyone know

00:41:16.510 --> 00:41:18.070
the way I'm making money.

00:41:19.740 --> 00:41:21.010
If Xiaoyu

00:41:21.190 --> 00:41:23.320
stays with us,

00:41:23.760 --> 00:41:25.550
it might put me in danger.

00:41:28.680 --> 00:41:30.230
So I've decided

00:41:30.230 --> 00:41:33.030
to send Xiaoyu away for a while.

00:41:37.130 --> 00:41:40.260
The doctor said I don't need
a kidney transplant yet.

00:41:40.360 --> 00:41:42.800
You don't need to do dangerous things.

00:41:42.860 --> 00:41:43.490
Yes.

00:41:43.980 --> 00:41:45.540
The doctor did say that.

00:41:46.030 --> 00:41:46.720
But,

00:41:46.740 --> 00:41:48.100
look, the doctor also said

00:41:48.100 --> 00:41:49.020
"yet."

00:41:50.190 --> 00:41:51.190
It's only for now.

00:41:52.000 --> 00:41:54.000
We have to face this sooner or later.

00:41:58.500 --> 00:42:00.260
Jiajia, remember one thing.

00:42:00.280 --> 00:42:01.360
In this world,

00:42:02.010 --> 00:42:03.050
except for me,

00:42:04.190 --> 00:42:06.800
no one will treat you well for no reason.

00:42:08.070 --> 00:42:10.470
What do we do
when we encounter difficulties?

00:42:10.470 --> 00:42:12.330
We can only solve them with money.

00:42:13.230 --> 00:42:14.660
So I have to do something.

00:42:17.300 --> 00:42:18.900
As for Xiaoyu,

00:42:19.250 --> 00:42:20.250
I can promise you.

00:42:21.760 --> 00:42:23.550
When I've dealt with all the problems

00:42:23.550 --> 00:42:24.610
and made the money,

00:42:25.400 --> 00:42:26.630
I'll take you with me

00:42:26.630 --> 00:42:27.590
to pick up Xiaoyu.

00:42:27.590 --> 00:42:28.590
We'll go to a...

00:42:29.190 --> 00:42:30.550
a new place to live.

00:42:31.360 --> 00:42:32.760
To live a good life there.

00:42:34.550 --> 00:42:36.550
Xiaoyu is our family's benefactor.

00:42:36.960 --> 00:42:38.490
We'll always be good to her.

00:42:39.700 --> 00:42:41.230
Why is Xiaoyu

00:42:41.230 --> 00:42:43.000
our family's benefactor?

00:42:50.710 --> 00:42:57.300
